<div class="section_title">A New Home for Innovations Plus at the Sands</div>
<span class="text">
It’s always exciting to have a new home. At the 2006 International CES, the emerging, embedded and digital imaging technologies will be living in an impressive new place—Innovations Plus at the Sands Expo and Convention Center. Innovations Plus at the Sands will feature some of the hottest new destinations and technologies at the International CES. 
<P>This is the place consumer technology decision makers at the show will head straight&nbsp;for to get a feel for what's on the horizon.&nbsp;Putting emerging and enabling technologies all under one roof will make it easier than ever for emerging technologies buyers, suppliers and developers to meet face to face. The show floor will be organized to provide an unprecedented opportunity for attendees to shop across categories and to diversify their product mix. </P>
<P>Truly a show-within-a-show, Innovations Plus at the Sands will house: </P>
<UL>
<LI>Flash Forward 3.0: Bringing Digital Imaging Into Focus </LI>
<LI><A href="/attendees/awards/innovations/default.asp">CES Innovations 2006 Design and Engineering Showcase and Best of Innovations</A> </LI>
<LI><A href="/press/events/default.asp#1485">CES Unveiled Press Showcase</A> </LI>
<LI>HD Pro Showcase </LI>
<LI>Studio@Home </LI>
<LI><A href="/exhibitors/space/techzones.asp">International CES TechZones</A>, select partner programs and retail training</LI></UL>
<P>Here are a few additional facts about this great new destination at the 2006 International CES:</P>
<UL>
<LI>Innovations Plus at the Sands is adjacent to the Venetian Hotel and near other great hotels on the Strip, including Treasure Island, Mirage, Harrah’s, New Frontier, Stardust and the <EM><STRONG>new </STRONG></EM>Wynn Las Vegas, opening this spring. </LI>
<LI>Transportation is free and easy with complimentary shuttle service to and from the Sands and all official International CES hotels. (The Sands Express shuttle travels between the Sands and the Las Vegas Convention Center every 15 minutes on show days.) </LI>
<LI>Outbound airport shuttle to McCarran International Airport January 7-8, 2006, just $5.00 per person. </LI>
<LI>Sands parking is available at the New Frontier, with complimentary shuttle service during move-in, show and move-out hours. The Venetian has valet and self-parking facilities for its hotel guests. </LI></UL>
<P>Look for feature stories on Innovations Plus at the Sands every month in <EM>The Exhibitor’s Source</EM>. See you there!</P>
</span>
