<div class="section_title">Get the Exposure and Recognition You Deserve with a CEA Sponsorship</div>
<span class="text">
We all want the very best exposure and recognition we can get. Your company’s brand can be a star when you become a sponsor of a CEA event. You’ll meet industry leaders in specialized, focused environments that lead to useful relationships and well-deserved recognition for your company. CEA has two great events scheduled in the next few months. 
<P>In May, CEA will host the PARA Management Conference for the first time. Hundreds of dealers will be there representing specialty audio-video, custom installation and home theater; these&nbsp;professionals are key to the growth of the CE industry. The CEO Summit, slated for June, is a tried and true classic. Entering its ninth year, this special event&nbsp;offers an executive-only environment where industry leaders focus on the most important issues in the CE industry today. </P>
<P>Take advantage of a CEA Sponsorship opportunity. Put your brand out front and get recognized. Please contact Wendy Hudak at (770) 643-7144 or <A href="mailto:whudak@CE.org">whudak@CE.org</A>. </P>
<P><A href="http://www.ce.org/events/event_info/default.asp?eventID=PARA05" target=_blank>2005 PARA Management Conference</A> <BR>May 11 - 15, 2005 <BR>Hotel del Coronado Coronado, CA<BR><BR><A href="http://www.ce.org/events/event_info/default.asp?eventID=CEO05" target=_blank>The 9th Annual Consumer Electronics CEO Summit </A><BR>June 22 - 25, 2005 <BR>The Broadmoor Colorado Springs, CO</P>
</span>
