<div class="section_title">Call for Speakers</div>
<span class="text">
With another CES successfully under our belts, it’s no time to rest on our laurels. We need to start focusing on speaking opportunities for the 2006 International CES. As a speaker at the CES, you’ll be the recipient of invaluable experience that allows you to interact with some of the most influential players in the tech world, while gaining invaluable exposure for your company. 
<P>The official 2006 International CES Call for Speakers (CFS) will be issued in May. If you would like to be notified when the CFS opens please send an e-mail to Megan West at <A href="mailto:mwest@CE.org">mwest@CE.org</A>&nbsp;with "CFS" in the subject line. </P>
</span>
