<div class="section_title">SINOCES</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=78 hspace=8 src="/images/partners/SINOCES_small.gif" width=120 align=right>CEA has partnered with the China Electronic Chamber of Commerce to expand SINOCES, the only government-sanctioned consumer electronics tradeshow in China. 
<P>More than 60,000 people from around the world attended last year's show. More than 300 vendor companies exhibited in 2004, including many who also exhibit at the International CES. The show will take place July 1-4, 2005, Qingdao, China. If you are interested in exhibiting, please contact&nbsp;Kirk Smallwood&nbsp;at <A href="mailto:ksmallwood@CE.org">ksmallwood@CE.org</A>.</P>
</span>
