<LI>Overall attendee satisfaction with the show increased to <STRONG>88 percent</STRONG> in 2005, up from 86 percent in 2004.</LI>
<LI><STRONG>89 percent </STRONG>of International attendees had an excellent or good experience at the show. </LI>
<LI><STRONG>80 percent </STRONG>of International attendees believed that CES provides all/most CE products. </LI>
<LI><STRONG>81 percent </STRONG>of U.S. attendees felt that CES provides all/most products.</LI></UL>
